anyone have tips that can help me stop procrastinating i procrastinate for everything until the last minute how can i change this well don't beat yourself up over it it doesn't help remember you can always try to stop procrastinating again later be kinder to yourself than you would a friend or stranger first i like to start by analyzing why it is i am procrastinating that usually takes a little time but occassionally provides some insight for example i stopped procrastinating on projects involving a long term friend of mine when i realized what an energy drain she was on me we are still friends we just don't speak as often and i only agree to work an occassional project with her which i do timely i like her company better in doses when it's something i really don't want to do i pretend that i am have to hurry to get it done because soon whatever time line fits some expected person will come by to either a notice and be proud of my accomplishment s and reward me or b will give me the really disappointed sad look i'm a sucker for the sad puppy look i sometimes have to use this external imaging to get the internal motivation with a necessary but unpleasant task usually giving myself an actual reward if i get stuff done helps an activity i like or inactivity like some time off procrastination is a habit for most people who use it however it can also be a sign of depression many people go through life with a slight depression and don't even realize the effect it is having on their lives consider this if you haven't before speak with a physician if you have questions healthcare and procrastination don't make a good long term partnership Procrastination Social psychology Theory of conduct Social rule Shaggy dog story Clinical depression Friends Adult attention-deficit disorder Time Out of Mind Gifted Piccolo Junior Saga K' Fight Club Kurt Cobain Borderline personality disorder Anxiety Psychosis Electrophysiology Theodicy Goodness and value theory Surveillance Similarities 